data.description: Welcome to your own little slice of country living just moments from access to Rt 7. Upon entering this lovingly maintained spacious home you are greeted with a cozy living room, down the hall you will find a beautiful dining room with built-in display shelves. Through the french doors off of the dining room you enter the open concept kitchen featuring a large island and an additional living room with fireplace. Beyond the kitchen you will find the laundry/utility room, a full bathroom, and two bedrooms with spacious closets. On the opposite side of the home you will find a gorgeous primary suite with a large walk-in closet, a beautiful bathroom with a deep tub and walk-in shower and an additional room that has been used as an office but would make an amazing additional walk-in closet, get ready room or even another bedroom if needed! On the front of the home is a newly built large front porch, around back is a lovely deck great for entertaining, a fire-pit and a shed perfect for storage. This home is just waiting for you! Schedule your showings today!
